snippet.title: Amber Scholl Makeup Line x Hush Collection|First Look, Swatches & Demo on Darkskin👩🏾💎
snippet.description:
Please Read❗️❗️❗️

Hi everyone in this video we will be discovering this collection together. Is it Brown Skin Friendly?? Hows the Quality?🤔🤔 Watch to find out! This is my honest opinion. Get you a snack bc this will be a long one! Enjoy!🙂💄
FYI: I have a phobia to extreme glitter since i was a child so this shall be interesting lol😂
Heyy #AmberScholl im doin this for u girl if you ever see this video! Lol (me dreaming)

❗️Please watch my video in the highest quality! 
Steps:
-open a video & in the upper right hand corner if on a apple device(it may be the same for all devices) click the 3dots & choose the gear ⚙️ icon which says Quality & choose 1080p or 720p. Whatever your device supports as the highest quality. Thanks a bunch! This goes for all Youtube videos🙂Enjoy!

If you read all this drop a 🎉emoji in the comment section!
